    "description": "從相關理論與實務中瞭解教具對幼兒發展的影響，並且訓練學生自製教學教具及研發創意教具的能力。",
    "prerequisites": "",
    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1.幼兒教具製作之相關理論與原理。<br>2.幼兒身體動作與健康領域教具之製作與應用。<br>3.幼兒認知領域教具之製作與應用。<br>4.幼兒語文領域教具之製作與應用。<br>5.幼兒社會領域教具之製作與應用。<br>6.幼兒情緒領域教具之製作與應用。<br>7.幼兒美感領域教具之製作與應用。<br>",
        "en": "1. To learn the theories and principles of making teaching aids for young children.<br>2. Design and application of body movement and health teaching aids.<br>3. Design and application of cognition teaching aids.<br>4. Design and application of language arts teaching aids.<br>5. Design and application of social studies teaching aids.<br>6. Design and application of emotion teaching aids.<br>7. Design and application of aesthetic feeling teaching aids.<br>"
